</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/unwirelife/~4/82yUowE-sdI" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>]]></content:encoded><feedburner:origLink>https://unwire.hk/2021/09/23/review-ehealth-app/life-tech/health/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=review-ehealth-app</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>【評測】METAL ROBOT魂巴巴托司狼式，配件豐富＋關節緊實</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/unwirelife/~3/Rv08ECMeRO0/</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Chris]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 23 Sep 2021 08:30:36 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[玩具]]></category><category><![CDATA[Bandai]]></category><category><![CDATA[高達]]></category><category><![CDATA[高達巴巴托司]]></category><category><![CDATA[高達巴巴托司狼式]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1053491</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>近日 Bandai 推出 METAL ROBOT 魂系列的最新產品高達巴巴托司狼式，今次的定價在 METAL  [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">近日 Bandai 推出 METAL ROBOT 魂系列的最新產品高達巴巴托司狼式，今次的定價在 METAL ROBOT 魂系列中相對較為親民，亦較容易入手。事不宜遲，就讓小編與大家一起看看這隻高達巴巴托司狼式有何特別吧。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054954 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0116unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0116unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0116unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0116unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054961 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0031unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0031unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0031unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0031unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054962 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0032unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0032unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0032unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0032unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054959 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0006unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0006unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0006unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0006unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054960 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0028unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0028unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0028unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0028unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054933 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0041unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0041unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0041unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0041unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054964 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0066unwire-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0066unwire-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0066unwire-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0066unwire-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>盒內配件豐富，配有黑白說明書</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">一打開盒可見有兩盒不同的配件，當中包括本體以及非常豐富的武裝配件，例如是眼部發光的特效件還有替換手型等。而在第二層則備有地台支架以及兩把龐大的大劍。另外，亦備有黑白印刷的產品說明書。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054932 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0053unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0053unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0053unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0053unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>重184g可動度足夠，腰部關節緊實</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">今次的狼式的重量是 184g，基本的可動度足夠，關節的鬆緊度亦無大問題。腰部關節與手臂同樣相當緊實，完全沒有鬆動的情況。而腰部和胯部之間使用球形關節連接，由於今次的狼式將球形關節下方的球碗做得非常大，因此接觸面積更多，便令腰部關節的緊實度進一步提升。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054934 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0057unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0057unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0057unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0057unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>小編最愛連動液壓桿，其他純裝飾沒實際作用</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而小編最喜歡的就是腰部左右兩根的液壓桿細節非常仔細，並設有連動設計，而全身上下其他的液壓桿亦未設有連動。例如曲肘後以及屈膝關節後的液壓桿亦只是純粹裝飾，並沒有實際作用。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054940 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0067unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0067unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0067unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0067unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054936 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0069unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0069unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0069unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0069unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>其餘可動結構仔細，造型不錯</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而這隻狼式身上亦另設有其餘的可動結構，例如胸前駕駛艙的展開結構，胸前的藍色裝甲可往前移動一小段距離，但並不能完全展開，當中也沒有座椅或是駕駛員等細節。而肩甲邊上也備有獨立的可動設計，肩甲邊的紅色裝甲可以獨立往外翻，而紅色裝甲上還有鐵華團的標誌，同時亦用上立體刻畫技術，造型相當不錯。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054938 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0083unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0083unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0083unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0083unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>背後數洞可裝武器，前踢幅度大</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而這隻狼式的頭部亦有所改變，狼式的天線上方是一圈連在一起的。背後背包的中間還備有可稍微抬起一定幅度的推進器，而背包的兩側有兩個洞，主要用於安裝武器，而之後會介紹的不少武器均可以安裝在這兩個洞上。同時，後裙甲上亦有一個洞，與上述兩個洞的大小是一樣的，不但同樣可以安裝武器，更可用於安裝支架。而狼式的大腿和襠部之間會多出一段關節，讓腿部向前踢的幅度變得更大。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054941 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0081unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0081unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0081unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0081unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054942 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0086unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0086unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0086unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0086unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>全身上下塗裝，印刷細節精緻</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">今天開箱的這一款高達巴巴托司狼式，全身上下基本上都是塗裝。除了金屬零件外，便鮮少有成型色零件。不過大面積塗裝亦是 METAL ROBOT 魂系列的傳統及特色。今次的狼式相當白淨，有點像是「新機出廠」的感覺。不過狼式身上的紅色注意符號倒是沒有偷懶，該移印的地方均有移印，感覺還是相當精緻的。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054937 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0052unwire-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0052unwire-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0052unwire-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0052unwire-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>雙眼特效件 6關節可調整</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">接下來的便到介紹相當豐富的武器配件。首先，盒內包括有一個替換的天線，主要用於實現雙眼發光的效果。而這個雙眼的特效件相較於以往的產品夫升了自由度，其中一個較大的改變便是加入了可動關節。而這個變化使得玩家可以根據擺放動作的不同，從而對特效件的方向作出調整。而一件特效件備有三個球形關節，兩側加在一起總共有 6 個球形關節以調整角度。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054943 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0074unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0074unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0074unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0074unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054944 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0047unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0047unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0047unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0047unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>大劍非常「巨大」 拿在手上沒違和感</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">之後，更備有不少武器，當中最令小編印象深刻的便是非常巨大的大劍，體積大到普通人拿在手上亦沒有任何違和感，真的相當相當「巨大」。而劍把的末端設有一段延伸關節，讓大劍可以變得更長，來呈現雙手握持的狀態。而大劍是備有塗裝的配件，中間採用黑鐵色，而劍刃處則用上銀色，看上去相當有真實感。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054945 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0064unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0064unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0064unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0064unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054946 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0084unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0084unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0084unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0084unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>另一把劍為鐵華團專屬，分開關節可手持</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而另外一把大劍與上者比起來的話便會較為小一點。而這把大劍是鐵華團專屬的武器，因此在劍身中間畫有鐵華團的標誌，並同樣備有塗裝。這把劍的劍把處有一個關節可以分開，只要透過這位置並將其放到對應的手型中便可以做到手持的狀態。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054947 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0051unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0051unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0051unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0051unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>兩枝砲無法同時安裝，可向後扭藏起</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">另外，還有兩個相當迷你的小錘，亦有兩個裝在手臂後面的武器，包括 200mm 炮及榴彈砲。而榴彈砲的口徑會比 200mm 炮更粗一點。而槍管位置亦有一些黑鐵色的塗裝。不過這兩枝砲無法同時安裝，只能擇其一。安裝時需要透過在手臂的後面安裝連接件，然後才廳把炮管安裝上去。而連接件的根底部有一個滑軌，讓玩家可以向前滑亦可以往後縮，而在不用時只要將其扭轉 180 度藏到手臂後面便可。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054950 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0048unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0048unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0048unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0048unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054951 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0044unwire-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0044unwire-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0044unwire-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0044unwire-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>背後二洞還原待機，全副武裝相當霸氣</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">而在背後也會有兩個同樣的洞，但不同的是這兩個洞是用於轉插接口的。轉接口可以安裝大劍等武器，來還原待機的狀態。而當全部武裝上身後，可說是非常霸氣，雖然劇中未有這樣出現過，但模型便可自行實現全副武裝的狀態。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054966 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0016unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0016unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0016unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0016unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054965 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0036unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0036unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0036unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0036unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><strong>總結：配件豐富，關節緊實</strong></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">今日開箱分享的 METAL ROBOT 魂系列高達巴巴托司狼式算是相當不錯，武器配件相當豐富，而且全身上下不少配件採用塗裝，並配有金屬骨架。而且關節緊實，把玩的手感亦相當不錯，不會有非常鬆動的感覺。而且官方定價更比以往產品便宜 30% 左右。因此有不少網民均指這是 Bandai 良心之作，但是不是良心之作便見仁見智，小編在此亦不討論太多，但仍然相當推薦有興趣的朋友入手看看。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054963 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0042unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0042unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0042unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0042unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054957 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0120unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0120unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0120unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0120unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="size-medium wp-image-1054958 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0002unwire-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0002unwire-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0002unwire-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/08/0002unwire.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p></p><div class="feedflare">
